{"tid":164754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暗角七警】曾健超帶笑步入覊留室服刑。","createTime":"2017-03-21T01:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T02:20:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb17eed25baa5e38e801d3116b292c4ebd75260","tid":164754,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170321/large/1490059824_2ccb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170321%2Flarge%2F1490059824_2ccb.jpg&h=4a630389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年佔領運動期間「暗角七警」的主角公民黨前成員曾健超，因向警員潑水及拒捕，去年5月被裁定襲警及拒捕罪成判囚5星期，一直獲准保釋等候上訴的他，今在法院提出棄上訴，將正式服刑。在扣除假期後，曾須服刑31天。曾在開庭前與律師文浩正擁抱，並跟一直協助他的立法會議員陳淑莊握手，隨後臉帶笑容步入犯人欄。法官親自向曾確認，問及是否自願，曾答：「是」，隨即臉露歡顏的步入覊留室服刑。<br />\n<br />\n曾在步入犯人欄前，亦已除下耳上的耳環、西裝上的黃絲別針。有女市民在庭上高叫：「阿ken支持你」，庭上約三十多人跟曾揮手送別。有女市民喊，旁邊人則安忌慰：「唔好喊，要笑，佢係為公義入獄嘛」。"},{"pid":"9e5c47b6ed79b60cca8e2bce9f46fe66a48b28b2","tid":164754,"uid":48735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"但係佢唔係選委咩..?"},{"pid":"c0e837ccb9949069818fea65ea7036245c9e67b5","tid":164754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8631ff9b42aeda061082265d024e7c5375f8fb93","tid":164754,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係佢唔係選委咩..?</blockquote><br />\n入左去都可以安排佢投票"},{"pid":"5cbf084dd3ba5344d60fa1793f54c6c7a534a5aa","tid":164754,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係佢唔係選委咩..?</blockquote><br />\n入左去都可以安排佢投票</blockquote><br />\n入到去無比人屌當贏"},{"pid":"565be2ed8440ea4915301201f1c534887e5ff030","tid":164754,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但係佢唔係選委咩..?</blockquote><br />\n入左去都可以安排佢投票</blockquote><br />\n入到去無比人屌當贏</blockquote><br />\n唔係話政治犯無乜人搞咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}